Classes in org.epochx.ge.op.init that implement Operator
 class FixedLengthInitialiser
          Initialisation implementation which constructs each program's chromosome to a specified length with a random sequence of codons.
 class FullInitialiser
          Initialisation implementation which constructs each program's chromosome while ensuring that it maps to a full parse tree of the specified depth.

 class RampedHalfAndHalfInitialiser
